      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that's ready for its next chapter? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and still has plenty of life left in it! While you'll notice some typical cosmetic wear and signs of previous adventures, it remains a reliable choice for your daily needs. It\u2019s a great opportunity to get a solid, functional car at a price that makes sense!",
