    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a practical option for a driver who prioritizes utility over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car would benefit from a routine service soon. On the exterior, you will find several noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and some clear coat peeling on the hood. The interior shows typical wear for its age, including some staining on the upholstery and minor cracking on the dashboard. It remains a solid, drivable vehicle that just needs a little extra care to reach its full potential.",
