    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine struggles to maintain a consistent idle and will require a full mechanical diagnostic, while the transmission shows significant hesitation during gear changes. Externally, the body has several noticeable dents, clear coat failure, and some rust spots on the wheel wells. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics, including the radio and power windows, are currently non-functional.",
