    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
