    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example is mechanically robust, featuring a recently completed VANOS overhaul and a comprehensive valve shim adjustment to ensure optimal timing and compression. The chassis has been properly addressed with rear subframe reinforcement, a critical preventative measure for this platform. The M-Variable limited-slip differential remains tight, providing excellent traction out of corners. While the finish shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with a dedicated driver's car, the suspension bushings and cooling system have been refreshed to maintain peak handling and thermal efficiency. A high-revving, analog masterpiece ready for the enthusiast.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
