    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, presenting in impressive condition throughout. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish with only the most minor signs of careful use, while the alloy wheels remain crisp and free of major scuffs. Inside, the cabin is a clean, smoke-free environment; the seats are supportive with minimal wear, and all electronic features\u2014including the premium audio and climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth, consistent power, backed by a comprehensive service history that proves its mechanical health. It drives straight and true, offering a tight, rattle-free experience on the road. This is a reliable, high-quality car that bridges the gap between everyday utility and refined comfort, ready for immediate enjoyment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
